@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title Pareto前沿与Hypervolume示意图（概念图，非当前核心实现）

scale 1.5

rectangle "目标空间" as Space #F5F5F5 {
  
  skinparam objectBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  skinparam objectBorderColor #333333
  
  object "参考点 r" as Ref {
    (最差Accuracy, 最差Latency)
  }
  
  object "候选A" as A {
    高Accuracy\n低Latency
  }
  
  object "候选B" as B {
    中Accuracy\n中Latency
  }
  
  object "候选C" as C {
    低Accuracy\n高Latency
  }
  
  object "候选D" as D {
    中Accuracy\n低Latency
  }
  
  object "候选E" as E {
    低Accuracy\n中Latency
  }
}

A -[hidden]-> B
B -[hidden]-> D
D -[hidden]-> A

C -[hidden]-> E
E -[hidden]-> Ref
Ref -[hidden]-> C

note right of A
  **Pareto前沿**: {A, B, D}
  A支配B? 否 (B latency更低)
  B支配D? 否 (D accuracy更高)
  A支配C? 是
  D支配E? 是
end note

note bottom of Ref
  该图用于说明目标优化语义：
  Pareto / Hypervolume 仍主要是
  文档与研究层概念。

  当前 MHE 实现的核心优化信号
  仍以标量 fitness、trigger、
  convergence 与 Bayesian search 为主。
end note

@enduml
